@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_chizaz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((0.12 + (v1 + 0.97 + v2 + 0.67)))
    v1 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = wp.exp(v1)
    v0 = (v1 + ((v2 + 0.37 / v1 + 0.46) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.16)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.70 / v1 + 0.88)) * (v1 + (v1 + 0.31 - v0 + 0.42)))
    data[tid] = v0
